    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''I kept thinking how life is cheap, how so many innocent people are killed.''</p>
        <p>HADI FARIS, whose son Hamza, 11, was one of 34 boys killed in a 2005 suicide bombing in Baghdad. [16]</p>
